ConsistencyStatus

class hets.ConsistencyStatus(hs_cons_status: hs.HetsAPI.Internal.ConsStatus)[source]

Consistency status of a node.

The status contains the required consistency as well as the result of a proven consistency (or UNKNOWN by default)

Warning:

This class should not be instantiated manually.
